n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Three Dragon Age Veilguard party members square up against a dragon before release time\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: BioWare/Electronic Arts\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/dragon-age-veilguard-release-time.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">This is not a trick: <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/dragon-age-the-veilguard/440892\">Dragon Age: The Veilguard</a></em> finally drops on Halloween, a treat for fans of a fantasy series that has gone untouched for about a decade.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Heres <strong>when <em>Dragon Age: The Veilguard</em> releases</strong> in your time zone, plus a bit about what to expect from the game.</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-none\">Dragon Age: The Veilguard release time and date in your time zone</h2>", "id": 1409013, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/dragon-age-veilguard-guides/469866/release-time-date-est-pst-bst", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "What time does Dragon Age: The Veilguard release?", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-29T11:59:14+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: ConcernedApe\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24992419/ss_6422d297347258086b389e3d5d9c0e0c698312e4.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em>Stardew Valley</em> was released just under 9 years ago, and developer Eric \u201cConcernedApe\u201d Barone finally unlocked one of the game\u2019s hardest achievements, allowing him to reach 100% completion on his farming life simulator. \u201cFinally got 100% achievements in <em>Stardew Valley</em>,\u201d Barone posted on X Tuesday, with a photo of the 100% unlocked achievements. The last achievement Barone needed to complete the game was \u201cFector\u2019s Challenge,\u201d which requires the player to beat in-game minigame <em>Journey of the Prairie King</em> without dying.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">On Stea", "id": 1409014, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/news/471780/stardew-valley-concernedape-100-percent-achievements", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Stardew Valley developer ConcernedApe finally 100%-ed his game", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-29T11:38:07+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"A closeup of the Turtle Beach Stealth Pivot wireless gaming controller in its standard layout.\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/Turtle-Beach-Stealth-Pivot-close-up-purple-bkgd.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">A couple years back, Victrix released a gaming controller with swappable front buttons. The <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2022/10/5/23388978/pdp-victrix-pr